1. Admin home page should give a status / activity overview. Recent unviewed comments etc.

2. Recent comments (that haven't yet been viewed), are shown on the front page of the administration site. Once a comment has been viewed by the photographer, it is considered *opened* and is pulled off of the front page (no longer new).

3. Recent comments (that haven't yet been viewed), are shown on the front page of the client site. Once a comment has been viewed by the client, it is considered *opened* and is pulled off of the front page (no longer new).

4. Allow sharing of booking pictures temporarily. Invite a friend to view your booking photos etc.

5. Apply a templating language
